title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: You may feel like a kid heading off to your exciting first day of school again with all the changes to your routines. Your day seems to hum and drum along with possibilities rather than be ho-hum while the stimulating Libra New Moon glides through your 6th House of Habits. But lets be clear: any significant improvements occur because youre making them happen, and not anyone else. Enjoy calling the shots and embrace these shifts as experiments. Consistency arrives only after youre satisfied with your results. Nothing is written in stone and its fine to switch everything up tomorrow. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
